"{0:d5}" -f 1234
> 01234
"{0:n3}" -f 123.45678
> 123.457

'server1' -replace '[,]', '[;]' **replaces comas with simicollons**

$profile -split '\.' **splits on periods**
-csplit **casesensitive**
"cat", "dog" -join
> catdog

